                    <p className="text-gray-600 mb-3">A leading global source for news, intelligence and conversation for the marketing and media community.</p>
                    <a href="https://adage.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" className="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 font-semibold">
                        Visit AdAge.com &rarr;
